  * [http://www.sslu.or.kr/zbbs/zboard.php?no=40744&id=bbs_free&page=1&sn1=&divpage=6&sn=off&ss=on&sc=on&select_arrange=headnum&desc=asc 분할 민영화의 거짓과 허상]
